# ElevenLabs TTS

- Follow agent skill: `.cursor/skills/elevenlabs/text-to-speech/SKILL.md`
- API key setup: `.cursor/skills/elevenlabs/setup-api-key/SKILL.md`
- Model: `eleven_flash_v2_5` only (credit conservation)
- Only `TtsService` may call ElevenLabs; use `@elevenlabs/elevenlabs-js` (not the deprecated `elevenlabs` package)
- Cache by sha256(text+voiceId+model); fixtures when `NODE_ENV=test|dev-offline`
- Enforce `TTS_DAILY_CHAR_BUDGET` before live synth
